    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA102-kiḷavi">itu kāmammikka kaḻipaṭar kiḷavi.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This the speech [situation] of exceeding affliction when desire had increased.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA102">
<l>            koṭuṅkural kuṟaitta cevvāyp paiṅkiḷi</l>
<l>            yañca lōmpi yārpataṅ koṇṭu</l>
<l>            niṉkuṟai muṭitta piṉṟai yeṉkuṟai</l>
<l>            colla vēṇṭumāl kaitoḻu tirappal</l>
<l>            palkōṭ palaviṉ cāra lavarnāṭṭu </l>
<l>            niṉkiḷai maruṅkiṟ cēṟi yāyi</l>
<l>            ṉammalai kiḻavōṟ kuraimati yimmalai</l>
<l>            kāṉak kuṟavar maṭamaka</l>
<l>            ḷēṉal kāva lāyiṉa ḷeṉavē.</l>
    </lg>
       <lg xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent">O red-mouthed green parakeets who shortened the bent ears,</l>
<l rend="indent">after you have fulfilled your need,</l>
<l rend="indent2">taking the opportunity of becoming full, avoiding fear,</l>
<l>it is necessary indeed to speak of my need. I beg [you] imploringly.</l>
<l rend="indent">When you go to your relations</l>
<l rend="indent2">in his land of jack trees with many [flower-]clusters,</l>
<l>talk to the lord of that mountain, to say</l>
<l rend="indent2">“the inexperienced daughter of the hill people from the forest</l>
<l rend="indent2">of this mountain has become one to guard the millet.”</l>
    </lg>
         </div>
